" />"},{"pid":"36b8e1336fae2dcdf6ea21891e58eb24b0344541","tid":2296512,"uid":268868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:34:02.000Z","msg":"本書買咗未睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53a4783c7dd248ff64ac2291ab111414e0605a7","tid":2296512,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0369d121d234f71ed4ddf3fe7cbcda923e20a355","tid":2296512,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:15:25.000Z","msg":"兒登仔：武肺弱感冒論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:42:55.000Z","msg":"最重要係有冇有力理據支持到呢個講法，我個人斷言唔到係咪一定錯。"},{"pid":"207490e22456a58156108b2669214b4a704009ce","tid":2296512,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"659bd591d3df000d1b53c8de24a7af47d878dd6b","tid":2296512,"uid":5150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2cf256abe0bd50715c1ddbf4caeff35825a8e11","tid":2296512,"uid":17335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3e0c886bf10e2b567482587dfb0d94e77336036e","tid":2296512,"uid":233118,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"睇完樓主篇文 好有共鳴<br />\n雖然可能唔太關專家事，但係確實感覺到身邊或者網絡上嘅人嘅「中上效應」同「確認偏誤」，即係自大主觀兼唔撚聽人講野。<br />\n一認真討論就會發現係用佢係先入為主，所有用嘅資料唔係為咗探討真相，單純為咗駁人，用事實辯駁就短暫耳聾或者不了了之，或者突然發難，九唔答八，唔係一種真正嘅討論。<br />\n依家都費事同人認真討論，大家鳩笑吓就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝巴打認真睇完！<br />\n<br />\n人嘅心理構造本身係咁，但教育可以修正我哋嘅呢種溝通困難，知道天外有天外，人外有人，同埋Fact嘅重要，學識咩叫理性溝通。但教育商品化之後，呢個作用已經愈嚟愈低。<br />\n<br />\n加埋，網路社交媒體演算法嘅影響，我哋反過嚟俾科技控制，強化咗溝通缺陷。基本上，現實傾計都比較okay，網路上係無咩可能說服到人，或者人哋會直接上升到hit and run嘅境界。<br />\n<br />\n要意識到自己有問題，係好困難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得基本邏輯（同語用嘅concept）應該要係中學必修"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:49:26.000Z","msg":"A rulebook for argument <br />\n中學生應該要讀"},{"pid":"1ce1cc1f370e0c4a70a790d41bbfef2d35336296","tid":2296512,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b53a4783c7dd248ff64ac2291ab111414e0605a7","tid":2296512,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0369d121d234f71ed4ddf3fe7cbcda923e20a355","tid":2296512,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:15:25.000Z","msg":"兒登仔：武肺弱感冒論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:42:55.000Z","msg":"最重要係有冇有力理據支持到呢個講法，我個人斷言唔到係咪一定錯。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:49:48.000Z","msg":"爆左成年有冇病理學家支持呢個講法<br />\n<br />\n兒登仔又有幾多醫科知識去論證<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4296a9e65cccb01a79d7df9a558f2a68d77d105","tid":2296512,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ce1cc1f370e0c4a70a790d41bbfef2d35336296","tid":2296512,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b53a4783c7dd248ff64ac2291ab111414e0605a7","tid":2296512,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0369d121d234f71ed4ddf3fe7cbcda923e20a355","tid":2296512,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:15:25.000Z","msg":"兒登仔：武肺弱感冒論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:42:55.000Z","msg":"最重要係有冇有力理據支持到呢個講法，我個人斷言唔到係咪一定錯。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:49:48.000Z","msg":"爆左成年有冇病理學家支持呢個講法<br />\n<br />\n兒登仔又有幾多醫科知識去論證<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"連登或者現代人好流行直覺立場為本，判斷事件。而唔係用理據去論證。呢個係最大嘅問題，思考嘅方式。"},{"pid":"cf8395e17d15791a122e280505d3997c7e168dba","tid":2296512,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4296a9e65cccb01a79d7df9a558f2a68d77d105","tid":2296512,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ce1cc1f370e0c4a70a790d41bbfef2d35336296","tid":2296512,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b53a4783c7dd248ff64ac2291ab111414e0605a7","tid":2296512,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:42:55.000Z","msg":"最重要係有冇有力理據支持到呢個講法，我個人斷言唔到係咪一定錯。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:49:48.000Z","msg":"爆左成年有冇病理學家支持呢個講法<br />\n<br />\n兒登仔又有幾多醫科知識去論證<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"連登或者現代人好流行直覺立場為本，判斷事件。而唔係用理據去論證。呢個係最大嘅問題，思考嘅方式。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:17:43.000Z","msg":"立場行先真相唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所謂嘅「真相」只係用嚟justify自己嘅立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當一個人限死咗自己喺同溫層唔出嚟只係會變咗自身起咗度防火牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉身無牆心中有牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf05e92b4ab8648c24272d336e7d847606fe0a88","tid":2296512,"uid":60648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫得好好<br />\n<br />\n講無知同陰謀論個度講得好好"},{"pid":"7db19da8a990b411091cf3aa26d60403d845e27c","tid":2296512,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4296a9e65cccb01a79d7df9a558f2a68d77d105","tid":2296512,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ce1cc1f370e0c4a70a790d41bbfef2d35336296","tid":2296512,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b53a4783c7dd248ff64ac2291ab111414e0605a7","tid":2296512,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:42:55.000Z","msg":"最重要係有冇有力理據支持到呢個講法，我個人斷言唔到係咪一定錯。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:49:48.000Z","msg":"爆左成年有冇病理學家支持呢個講法<br />\n<br />\n兒登仔又有幾多醫科知識去論證<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"連登或者現代人好流行直覺立場為本，判斷事件。而唔係用理據去論證。呢個係最大嘅問題，思考嘅方式。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:39:24.000Z","msg":"最慘弱感冒論既支持者唔係擁有足夠醫學知識同理論基礎去論證<br />\n<br />\n而家出於個人利益例如唔想限聚 唔想戴口罩 想去旅行享樂等等做出發點<br />\n<br />\n然後講講香港本土確診數字 死亡率等等就意圖去淡化疫情 忽略疫情仍然係全球爆發呢個事實<br />\n<br />\n而當你警惕 令佢哋冇得享樂 你就係恐懼撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ae84344431c4d9a4108d698801b8c52fd45b2a","tid":2296512,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08aebb18f31e0049fa48f38af2b4776aa0e8cbc5","tid":2296512,"uid":93437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T22:08:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>專家的失職，犯錯而不知改進，公民確是有權監察，加以批評，特別是當知識分子跨越自身領域之外，對其他範疇表達意見，而被視作權威。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係，其實好多專家都真係好專，基本上講十句有九句都必然係自身鑽研領域之外。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"巴打呢個問題，本書嘅意思係，唔好跳範疇去講專業意見。科學家可以講政治，但唔係專業。藝人可以講科學，老高可以講神秘學，運動員可以講法律，但都唔應該當係權威。<br />\n<br />\n當然好似巴打咁講，範疇之中，都各有所專。但普遍已經比範疇外嘅人識得多。"},{"pid":"1cd7ae0fffe08ebadbde9fa2a93538fee10e9303","tid":2296512,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T04:13:30.000Z","msg":"依個世界根本好多假專家，佢地根本唔熟悉佢自己個範疇，或者已經outdate咗好耐。"},{"pid":"f70d9dfff5cbefb5d684876681233aa9426b8097","tid":2296512,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T04:56:20.000Z","msg":"其實同樣理論都適應係我方陣營<br />\n蘋果立場等既主流媒體一定會帶來利好消息<br />\n而我地不斷吸收有利我方既野 漸漸就會困死左係一個回音壁入面<br />\n其實兩邊都睇 知道兩邊各自主張同利益<br />\n咁先可以知己知彼 百戰百勝"},{"pid":"6eca1270904f90f3d2949a185fd4ff39b1facd66","tid":2296512,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"520b50f890c3b05d95f6a946b7a78547021e72eb","tid":2296512,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f0216edeb19856375db25ba01a90ad647aadd70","tid":2296512,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"176434718225afe76d6289b2ddcc09ab7f1cc3ed","tid":2296512,"uid":73319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"我已改用brave 瀏覽器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阻截晒啲廣告同追蹤，眼不見為淨。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T17:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打覺得有咩唔同<br />\n聽到我都想轉嚟試試"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T17:16:57.000Z","msg":"同埋要習慣用DuckDuckGo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:56:05.000Z","msg":"之前用過一排<br />\n中文搜尋頗弱<br />\n成日搵啲殘體source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}